reviewText: Unique story about a planet of amazon women from outer space looking for an earthman virile enough to help them procreate. A sci-fi spoof featuring some of the well known ladies in the modeling and bodybuilding industry (including two personal friends - Jayne "Kasie Cavanaugh" Trcka, and Lauren Powers).
Simply terrible movie.  No real plot line, acting was awful - i have no idea why I even bought this DVD. Would not recommend unless you like silly sci - fi movies.
Acting is poor, filming is poor, but it is funny and sexy
